dict.string: $(PRODUCT_NAME) uses apple music access as part of its metadata analysis to enable your lender to assess whether you are a good fit. Metadata analysis does not look at your personal data. If you allow the app to share this non-personal data, it will be sent to YoYuu's scoring service.
